Modifications in this fork (2024-2026, DanilenkA):
  - Fixed broken upstream tools (get_alarms, get_vm_events, get_host_details)
  - Added real-time performance metrics via pyVmomi PerformanceManager
    (get_vm_metrics, get_host_metrics)
  - Added complete vSAN read-only monitoring suite (10 tools):
    * list_vsan_clusters
    * get_vsan_cluster_health
    * get_vsan_capacity_info
    * get_vsan_disk_groups
    * get_vsan_performance_metrics
    * get_vsan_health_checks
    * get_vsan_objects
    * get_vsan_storage_policies
    * get_vsan_capabilities
    * get_vsan_witness_info
  - Added vSAN helper methods in pyvmomi_client.py
    (get_vsan_vc_mos, find_vsan_cluster, is_vsan_enabled)
  - CA-aware SSL support
  - Sanitized public SKILL template (EXAMPLE_SKILL.md)

